N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4039.14 - Deposit may be forfeited

State Regulations

Before considering an objection, the stewards may
require a deposit of $25, which shall be forfeited if the objection is decided
to be frivolous or vexatious. Notes
